data.description: Options abound for the beautiful ranch style condo at the Amana Colonies Golf Course, hole 9's tee.  4 bedrooms each with it's own ensuite bathroom.  The unique set up allows for single family use or rental.  The home can be separated into 3 units and rented out individually or the entire unit can be rented as a long or short term rental.  the lower level family room has a walk out to the private, patio. The laundry is currently located in the utility room in the basement, but there is a 2nd set of laundry hookups in the hall closet on the main level (off the front entrance).  The unit is nestled into the timber with a beautiful deck overlooking the golf course.  AJA Estate Services will be have a sale at the property on Saturday, 12/9/23 from 9-5pm and Sunday, 12/10/23 from 10-4pm.  Stop by and check out out the condo and the amazing collection of items for sale.
